 -- Release Notes ---------------------------------------------------------->

  A legendary masterpiece returns

  Experience this acclaimed masterpiece with its renowned Sumi-e ink art 
  style in breathtaking high resolution.

  Take the role of Amaterasu, the Japanese sun goddess who inhabits the form 
  of a legendary white wolf Shiranui. Use magical abilities, attacks, and 
  Celestial Brush techniques to restore the land of Nippon to its previous 
  glory full of life and color.

  Not only can you play in both widescreen and and the original 4:3 aspect 
  ratio, you can now use the Joy-Con (in TV mode/tabletop mode) or touch 
  screen (in portable mode) for intuitive, direct Celestial Brush controls.

